# FOLLOW THESE STEPS :
 STEP 1 :
INSTALL PYTHON

STEP 2 : Verify Tkinter
python -m tkinter   ( TERMINAL OR CMD )

STEP 3 : Install Ollama CLI
Download from https://ollama.com/download and install for your OS

STEP 4 : Pull the Phi Model
ollama pull phi          (TERMINAL OR CMD)

STEP 5 : Install Python ollama Package 
pip install ollama         (TERMINAL OR CMD)

STEP 6 :
CREATE A FOLDER FOR YOUR PARAPHRASER 

STEP 7 :
OPEN VS CODE AND SELECT THE PARAPHRASE FOLDER AND CREATE TWO FILES NAMED PARAPHRASE.py and GUI.py

STEP 8 :
COPY AND PASTE THE CODE PROVIDED !
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

* NOTE:
THIS PARAPHRASER WAS BUILT FOR A PC WITH LOW-SPECS IF YOU GOT A PC WITH  16 or 32 gb ram with 16+ VRAM use Mistral instead of phi 
OR YOU CAN ALSO USE OPEN AI GPT (PAID).








